input:
-- start template query50.tpl query 60 in stream 0
select /* TPC-DS query50.tpl 0.60 */  
   s_store_name
  ,s_company_id
  ,s_street_number
  ,s_street_name
  ,s_street_type
  ,s_suite_number
  ,s_city
  ,s_county
  ,s_state
  ,s_zip
  ,sum(case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 30 ) then 1 else 0 end)  as "30 days" 
  ,sum(case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 30) and 
                 (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 60) then 1 else 0 end )  as "31-60 days" 
  ,sum(case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 60) and 
                 (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 90) then 1 else 0 end)  as "61-90 days" 
  ,sum(case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk > 90) and
                 (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk <= 120) then 1 else 0 end)  as "91-120 days" 
  ,sum(case when (sr_returned_date_sk - ss_sold_date_sk  > 120) then 1 else 0 end)  as ">120 days" 
from
   store_sales
  ,store_returns
  ,store
  ,date_dim d1
  ,date_dim d2
where
    d2.d_year = 2000
and d2.d_moy  = 8
and ss_ticket_number = sr_ticket_number
and ss_item_sk = sr_item_sk
and ss_sold_date_sk   = d1.d_date_sk
and sr_returned_date_sk   = d2.d_date_sk
and ss_customer_sk = sr_customer_sk
and ss_store_sk = s_store_sk
group by
   s_store_name
  ,s_company_id
  ,s_street_number
  ,s_street_name
  ,s_street_type
  ,s_suite_number
  ,s_city
  ,s_county
  ,s_state
  ,s_zip
order by s_store_name
        ,s_company_id
        ,s_street_number
        ,s_street_name
        ,s_street_type
        ,s_suite_number
        ,s_city
        ,s_county
        ,s_state
        ,s_zip
limit 100

query.query: /* START TEMPLATE QUERY50.TPL QUERY 60 IN STREAM 0 */ /* TPC-DS QUERY50.TPL 0.60 */ SELECT S_STORE_NAME , S_COMPANY_ID , S_STREET_NUMBER , S_STREET_NAME , S_STREET_TYPE , S_SUITE_NUMBER , S_CITY , S_COUNTY , S_STATE , S_ZIP , SUM ( CASE WHEN ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK <= 30 ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS "30 DAYS" , SUM ( CASE WHEN ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK > 30 ) AND ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK <= 60 ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS "31-60 DAYS" , SUM ( CASE WHEN ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK > 60 ) AND ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK <= 90 ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS "61-90 DAYS" , SUM ( CASE WHEN ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK > 90 ) AND ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK <= 120 ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS "91-120 DAYS" , SUM ( CASE WHEN ( SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK - SS_SOLD_DATE_SK > 120 ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END ) AS " > 120 DAYS" FROM STORE_SALES , STORE_RETURNS , STORE , DATE_DIM AS D1 , DATE_DIM AS D2 WHERE D2.D_YEAR = 2000 AND D2.D_MOY = 8 AND SS_TICKET_NUMBER = SR_TICKET_NUMBER AND SS_ITEM_SK = SR_ITEM_SK AND SS_SOLD_DATE_SK = D1.D_DATE_SK AND SR_RETURNED_DATE_SK = D2.D_DATE_SK AND SS_CUSTOMER_SK = SR_CUSTOMER_SK AND SS_STORE_SK = S_STORE_SK GROUP BY S_STORE_NAME , S_COMPANY_ID , S_STREET_NUMBER , S_STREET_NAME , S_STREET_TYPE , S_SUITE_NUMBER , S_CITY , S_COUNTY , S_STATE , S_ZIP ORDER BY S_STORE_NAME NULLS FIRST , S_COMPANY_ID NULLS FIRST , S_STREET_NUMBER NULLS FIRST , S_STREET_NAME NULLS FIRST , S_STREET_TYPE NULLS FIRST , S_SUITE_NUMBER NULLS FIRST , S_CITY NULLS FIRST , S_COUNTY NULLS FIRST , S_STATE NULLS FIRST , S_ZIP NULLS FIRST LIMIT 21
